SourceString: The secrets of <%sB_TARGET> have been released!
<%sB_TARGET> has gone back in full force!
<%sB_ACTOR> did not successfully extinguish the flames!
<%sB_ACTOR> has set up a magic circle.
The Angel Slime Tarot has moved to your hand!
An SSS rank tarot card has been moved to your hand!
<%sB_TARGET>'s HP and MP are fully recovered!
